---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Chat from '../components/Chat';
---

<BaseLayout title="Chat with Shreyas" description="Ask me anything about my thoughts, writing, or projects">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Chat with Shreyas</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
      This is an AI-powered chat interface that allows you to ask questions about my thoughts, opinions, and ideas based on the content from my blog. 
      It uses the Memory and Computation Protocol (MCP) to provide relevant and contextual responses.
    </p>
    
    <Chat client:load />
    
    <div class="mt-8 border-t border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 pt-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">About this AI Assistant</h2>
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p>
          This AI assistant is powered by the Memory and Computation Protocol (MCP), which allows it to retrieve and reason over 
          the content from my blog. It has been trained on my writing style and the topics I care about, enabling it to represent 
          my thoughts and perspectives.
        </p>
        <p>
          While it strives to accurately reflect my views, please understand that it may not perfectly capture the nuance of my thinking 
          on every topic. For the most authentic representation of my ideas, I encourage you to read my blog posts directly.
        </p>
        <p>
          All responses are generated using AI and the content from my published writing. The assistant doesn't have access to 
          personal or private information beyond what I've shared publicly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout> 